docs.text:
• ㊙️ The content is encrypted with AES-256 and is available to members only. Please contact the administrator for a username and password.
  • ⭐ Please see this page for basic information about this site and our group.

docs.title: About us
docs.text: We are a small group of researchers working on the design of AI, covering both hardware and software. More details can be found on the PI's research page. Please see this page for the list of members.

docs.title: Join us
docs.text: Please see this page for information on how to join our group.

docs.title: Suggested submission list
docs.text:
